Paper: hep-th/9512114

Date: 1995-12-15

Title: Chiral Symmetry Breaking by a Magnetic Field in Weak-coupling QED

Authors: C.N. Leung, Y.J. Ng, and A.W. Ackley

Comments: Latex; 11 pages

Using the nonperturbative Schwinger-Dyson equation, we show that chiralsymmetry in weak-coupling massless QED is dynamically broken by a constant butarbitrarily strong external magnetic field.